thread.title: Dr. Jane F. Bourgeois
thread.title_full: Fabletics reviewed by Dr. Jane F. Bourgeois

author: Dr. Jane F. Bourgeois
title: Dr. Jane F. Bourgeois
text: The Salar leggings live up to their description - the best 'stay put' material for working out in all angles, movements and with style! ;-) Other items that I have worn maintain fabric quality and elegance - from Barre classes to professional conferences 'pack in a flash' - comfort and style are found with quality material - I truly enjoy Fabletics. Thank you, Kate!
